<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<% include ./partials/head -%>
</head>
<body>

	<header>
		<% include ./partials/header -%>
	</header>

	<main class="container">
		<div class="row page-header">
			<div class="col-lg-12">
				<h1 class="white-font" style="font-size: 30px;">Starcups</h1>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-9">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
						<p class="rating white-font">
							<% for (var k=0; k<5; k++) { %>
							<% if (k < location.rating) { %>
							<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star"></span>
							<% } else { %>
							<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span>
							<% } %>
							<% } %>
						</p>
						<p class="white-font"><%= location.address %></p>
						<div class="panel panel-primary">
							<div class="panel-heading">
								<h2 class="panel-title white-font">Opening hours</h2>
							</div>
							<div class="panel-body" style="font-size: 24px;">
								<% for(var m=0; m<openingTimes.length; m++) { %>
								<p><%= openingTimes[m].days%> : <% if(openingTimes[m].closed) { %>closed<% } else { %>
									<%= openingTimes[m].open%> - <%= openingTimes[m].close%><% } %></p>
								<% } %>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="panel panel-primary">
							<div class="panel-heading">
								<h2 class="panel-title white-font">Facilities</h2>
							</div>
							<div class="panel-body">
								<% for(var j=0; j<location.facilities.length; j++) { %>
								<span class="label label-warning">
									<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok">
									</span>&nbsp;<%= location.facilities[j] %>
								</span>&nbsp;
								<% } %>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 location-map">
						<div class="panel panel-primary">
							<div class="panel-heading">
								<h2 class="panel-title white-font">Location Map</h2>
							</div>
							<div class="panel-body">
								<img src="http://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=51.455041,-0.9690884&amp;zoom=17&amp;size=400x350&amp;sensor=false&amp;markers=51.455041,-0.9690884&amp;scale=2" class="img-responsive img-rounded"/>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-xs-12">
						<div class="panel panel-primary review-panel">
							<div class="panel-heading">
								<a href="/location/addreview" class="btn btn-default pull-right">Add review</a>
								<h2 class="panel-title white-font">Customer Reviews</h2>
							</div>
							<div class="panel-body review-container">
								<% for(var r=0; r<reviews.length; r++) { %>
								<div class="row">
									<div class="review">
										<div class="well well-sm review-header">
											<span class="rating">
												<% for (var k=0; k<5; k++) { %>
												<% if (k < reviews[r]	.rating) { %>
												<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star"></span>
												<% } else { %>
												<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span>
												<% } %>
												<% } %>
											</span>
											<span class="reviewAuthor"><%= reviews[r].name%></span>
											<small class="reviewTimestamp"><%= reviews[r].date%></small>
										</div>
										<div class="col-xs-12">
											<p><%= reviews[r].comment%></p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<% } %>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-3 white-font">
				<p>Starcups is on Loc8r because it has accessible wifi and space to sit down with your laptop and get some work done.</p>
				<p>If you've been and you like it - or if you don't - please leave a review to help other people just like you.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
	<footer>
		<% include ./partials/footer -%>
	</footer>

</body>
</html>